  {id: 404, name: "strace_me", url: "https://rubygems.org/gems/strace_me", description: "A wrapper around strace(1) that allows you to perform targetted tracing of a\nblock.  strace_me allows you to track down problems without wading through\ngobs of ruby startup or other irrelevant noise."},
