  {id: 421, name: "tidy_table", url: "https://rubygems.org/gems/tidy_table", description: "TidyTable by Geoffrey Grosenbach http://topfunky.com  == DESCRIPTION:  Yet another library to convert an array of structs (such as an ActiveRecord  object) into an HTML table. Simple, with a few options. Includes automatic  tags for first_column, first_row, even, odd, etc."},
